<p>Soot Spirits is a responsive mobile ready lightweight two column Jekyll theme made with Bulma CSS. It is a great template for simple personal blogs with focus on typography.</p>

<h3 id="some-good-features">Some Good Features</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Fully mobile ready</li>
  <li>Built on top of Balma CSS</li>
  <li>Beautiful typography (uses League Gothic, Roboto and Open Sans</li>
  <li>Two column layout suitable for a wide range of blogging habits</li>
  <li>Fully customisable theme including the ‘hello’ text, quotes, nav items and sidebar widgets</li>
</ul>

